WEBVTT

00:10:29.994 --> 00:10:33.203
What about on the demand side?

00:10:33.227 --> 00:10:35.980
You know, there are generations
around the world

00:10:36.004 --> 00:10:38.060
who are being lost to war.

00:10:39.202 --> 00:10:42.193
It is possible to disrupt
that cycle of violence

00:10:42.217 --> 00:10:46.210
with investments in education,
in strengthening the rule of law

00:10:46.234 --> 00:10:48.615
and in economic development,
especially for women.

00:10:48.639 --> 00:10:50.267
I have personally seen

00:10:50.291 --> 00:10:53.332
just how incredibly powerful
those kinds of efforts can be

00:10:53.356 --> 00:10:54.690
around the world.

00:10:55.458 --> 00:10:56.834
But here's the thing:

00:10:56.858 --> 00:10:58.266
they take time,

00:10:58.290 --> 00:11:02.329
which means for you as individuals,
if you want to give,